"{\"uid\": \"chronline.com-stories-olympic-peninsula-fire-prompts-evacuation-notices,360176\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"A growing 150-acre wildfire in Jefferson County is threatening homes and has prompted fire officials to warn residents to prepare for potential evacuation if conditions worsen.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 176, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2620 fire  \\u2026  Unlock unlimited access for just $1 for your first month  Click here to start a digital subscription  To continue reading, you will need to either log in to your subscriber account, below, or purchase a new subscription.\", \"from\": 178, \"to\": 416, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are a print subscriber, but do not yet have an online account,click hereto create one.\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 511, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Click hereto see your options for becoming a subscriber.\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 569, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Click herecreate a free account for posting comments and events to our calendar.\", \"from\": 571, \"to\": 651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A growing 150-acre wildfire in Jefferson County is threatening homes and has prompted fire officials to warn residents to prepare for potential evacuation if conditions worsen.\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 829, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2620 fire near the town of Brinnon on the Olympic Peninsula started burning Wednesday evening near the Mount Jupiter area, according to the Brinnon Fire Department.\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 999, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 862, \"end\": 869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brinnon,_Washington\", \"score\": 0.9588348365752419, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brinnon\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brinnon,_Washington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brinnon,_Washington\"}, {\"begin\": 975, \"end\": 982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brinnon,_Washington\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brinnon\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brinnon,_Washington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brinnon,_Washington\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Washington State Patrol authorized state fire assistance for local firefighters working to contain the blaze on Thursday.\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1125, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1004, \"end\": 1027, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_State_Patrol\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Washington State Patrol\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_State_Patrol\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_State_Patrol\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is threatening homes, according to the Patrol.\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1175, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As of Thursday, the entire Duckabush area was under a Level 1 \\\"be alert\\\" evacuation notice while certain residents were under a Level 2 \\\"be ready\\\" notice, according to the Brinnon Fire Department, which initially responded to the fire.\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1412, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1349, \"end\": 1356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brinnon,_Washington\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brinnon\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brinnon,_Washington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brinnon,_Washington\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The fire, which is close to the Olympic National Forest, is moving northwest, but smoke could reach Seattle, depending on the wind patterns, Department of Natural Resources spokesperson Thomas Kyle-Milward said.\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1446, \"end\": 1469, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_National_Forest\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olympic National Forest\", \"types\": [\"Q473972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_National_Forest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_National_Forest\"}, {\"begin\": 1514, \"end\": 1521, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seattle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.1126425907979655e-17, \"text\": \"Seattle\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seattle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seattle\"}, {\"begin\": 1600, \"end\": 1606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Tank_Engine\", \"score\": 0.9996980179676562, \"rank\": 0.000264920728294981, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Tank_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Tank_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"DNR now has six aircraft on the fire as well as two hand crews, four engines and a Forest Service engine on the ground, he said.\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1754, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1626, \"end\": 1629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_State_Department_of_Natural_Resources\", \"score\": 0.577989760576891, \"rank\": 0.7082755302286101, \"text\": \"DNR\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_State_Department_of_Natural_Resources\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Washington_State_Department_of_Natural_Resources\"}, {\"begin\": 1709, \"end\": 1723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Forest_Service\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9863562173433265e-26, \"text\": \"Forest Service\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Forest_Service\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Forest_Service\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An origin location or cause for the fire was not available, Kyle-Milward said.\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1834, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's pretty dang smokey out there,\\\" Kyle-Milward said.\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1891, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Given the wind direction, there is an assumption that Seattle might get a little smoke.\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1980, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1947, \"end\": 1954, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seattle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.1126425907979655e-17, \"text\": \"Seattle\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seattle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seattle\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are not sure how much, but they are going to at least be able to smell it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 2059, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The fire is burning in a recently logged area with steep terrain and heavy fuels, according to an Incident Management Team news release.\", \"from\": 2061, \"to\": 2197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2159, \"end\": 2183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Incident_management_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Incident Management Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Incident_management_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Incident_management_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Crews on the ground are working to place lines around homes for protection.\", \"from\": 2198, \"to\": 2273, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Shelters have not been opened.\", \"from\": 2275, \"to\": 2305, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Residents evacuating and needing to shelter animals because of the fire should contact the Center Valley Animal Rescue in Quilcene.\", \"from\": 2306, \"to\": 2437, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2397, \"end\": 2410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Center_Valley,_Pennsylvania\", \"score\": 0.9976247030865579, \"rank\": 0.0009523809523812096, \"text\": \"Center Valley\", \"types\": [\"Q532\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Center_Valley,_Pennsylvania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Center_Valley,_Pennsylvania\"}, {\"begin\": 2428, \"end\": 2436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quilcene,_Washington\", \"score\": 0.9843231115469712, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Quilcene\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quilcene,_Washington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quilcene,_Washington\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tips when smoke worsens air quality  * Stay indoors when air quality levels are considered \\\"unhealthy,\\\" or when AQI levels exceed 150.\", \"from\": 2439, \"to\": 2573, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"People at higher risk from smoke - including children, those over 65, those with asthma or respiratory and heart conditions, and pregnant people - should stay indoors when AQI hits 100.\", \"from\": 2574, \"to\": 2759, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2746, \"end\": 2749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_quality_index\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.745043262895762e-32, \"text\": \"AQI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_quality_index\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_quality_index\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"* Limit physical activity outdoors, including physical labor, running, biking and sports, when smoke levels are \\\"unhealthy for sensitive groups,\\\" or measure over 100 AQI.\", \"from\": 2761, \"to\": 2931, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"* Watch for symptoms of smoke exposure.\", \"from\": 2933, \"to\": 2972, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Move people inside if they have a headache, sore throat or nose, cough, burning eyes, dizziness or wheezing.\", \"from\": 2973, \"to\": 3081, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"* Improve indoor air quality by closing windows and doors, unless it gets too hot, and setting up a HEPA or box fan filter.\", \"from\": 3083, \"to\": 3206, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3183, \"end\": 3187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HEPA\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"HEPA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HEPA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HEPA\"}, {\"begin\": 3191, \"end\": 3198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fan_(machine)\", \"score\": 0.999999839168153, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"box fan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fan_(machine)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fan_(machine)\"}, {\"begin\": 3199, \"end\": 3205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_filter\", \"score\": 0.9999999982373993, \"rank\": 1.5120182417542895e-09, \"text\": \"filter\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_filter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_filter\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"* Visit libraries, community centers, malls or other indoor spaces with air conditioning to stay cool.\", \"from\": 3208, \"to\": 3310, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"* Wear N95 or KN95 masks when outside.\", \"from\": 3312, \"to\": 3350, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They offer good protection from smoke for most people.\", \"from\": 3351, \"to\": 3405, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Visit st.news/WAtracker for interactive maps to track Washington wildfires and air quality.\", \"from\": 3407, \"to\": 3498, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3461, \"end\": 3471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Washington\", \"score\": 0.7215018119439207, \"rank\": 0.3859978249012268, \"text\": \"Washington\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Washington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Washington\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For additional information on air quality and smoke impacts near you, visit the website AirNow.gov or the Washington Smoke Blog, which is run by local, state and federal agencies.\", \"from\": 3500, \"to\": 3679, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3606, \"end\": 3616, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Washington\", \"score\": 0.7215018119439207, \"rank\": 0.3859978249012268, \